{"tid":423721,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"兩種人 邊種性格易相處d?","createTime":"2017-10-04T06:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T15:17:13.000Z","uid":8603,"like":6,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"323f04c4a2ba62b1fe53a7d25ec53febcf36aeea","tid":423721,"uid":8603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"好容易就會嬲，唔會忍人。但過一陣就可以好似乜事都冇。正正常常同你講野。<br />\n<br />\n激嬲佢你都唔會太驚，因為你知好快冇事，但郁啲就嬲好黑人憎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好難先會嬲，自己先容忍。但忍得耐。當一掂到佢底線就會嬲你一世。唔會有朋友做<br />\n<br />\n好難激嬲到佢，但你自己要慢慢搵佢條底線，小心踩地雷。"},{"pid":"7abc6744f4c425157cdd39c7bdb8c13a05d9bcf5","tid":423721,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:53:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"650af04c54ceb77423c3ba9eb98e12ea18c7ed40","tid":423721,"uid":8603,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:07:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊種係處先？</blockquote><br />\n講人 唔係講女"},{"pid":"9cd955d296ff5db4129b2c7a8a0fecf46ebc8a1b","tid":423721,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"前者"},{"pid":"66420c05e7d7cb0d5f041d7ecb45f9cf642f675c","tid":423721,"uid":103031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"前者 同人嗌交過一陣都會主動搵返人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88ed1f93df4cd751ec02ddb3aa1def63729efaa","tid":423721,"uid":130780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊種係處先？</blockquote><br />\n講人 唔係講女</blockquote><br />\n女都係人"},{"pid":"170fd0e225fe6f908a0c48ba464971497b102320","tid":423721,"uid":431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:37:07.000Z","msg":"女人對男人=前者<br />\n女人對女人=後者<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b74ced0cc47b0d2989a15a157305328f5934553","tid":423721,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"